snippet.title: PINEAPPLE: A Bittersweet Revenge - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Become the ultimate prankster by sneakily stashing pineapples in the most unlikely places until the bully goes crazy!

WISHLIST NOW ON STEAM! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2791360/PINEAPPLE_A_Bittersweet_Revenge/

Pineapple is a prank simulator inspired by a Reddit post, a short interactive mischief that uses humor and hand-drawn art to tell a revenge tale about the quirks of bullying.

For more info check here: https://peworks.info/portfolio-items/pineapple-2/
